{"thi-ap8:0.1":"Theriapadana ","thi-ap8:0.2":"Sumedhavagga ","thi-ap8:0.3":"Sattuppalamalikatheriapadana ","thi-ap8:1.1":"“Nagare arunavatiya, ","thi-ap8:1.2":"aruno nama khattiyo; ","thi-ap8:1.3":"Tassa ranno ahum bhariya, ","thi-ap8:1.4":"varitam varayamaham. ","thi-ap8:2.1":"Satta mala gahetvana, ","thi-ap8:2.2":"uppala devagandhika; ","thi-ap8:2.3":"Nisajja pasadavare, ","thi-ap8:2.4":"evam cintesi tavade. ","thi-ap8:3.1":"‘Kim me imahi malahi, ","thi-ap8:3.2":"sirasaropitahi me; ","thi-ap8:3.3":"Varam me buddhasetthassa, ","thi-ap8:3.4":"nanamhi abhiropitam’. ","thi-ap8:4.1":"Sambuddham patimanenti, ","thi-ap8:4.2":"dvarasanne nisidaham; ","thi-ap8:4.3":"‘Yada ehiti sambuddho, ","thi-ap8:4.4":"pujayissam mahamunim’. ","thi-ap8:5.1":"Kakudho vilasantova, ","thi-ap8:5.2":"migarajava kesari; ","thi-ap8:5.3":"Bhikkhusanghena sahito, ","thi-ap8:5.4":"agacchi vithiya jino. ","thi-ap8:6.1":"Buddhassa ramsim disvana, ","thi-ap8:6.2":"hattha samviggamanasa; ","thi-ap8:6.3":"Dvaram avapuritvana, ","thi-ap8:6.4":"buddhasetthamapujayim. ","thi-ap8:7.1":"Satta uppalapupphani, ","thi-ap8:7.2":"parikinnani ambare; ","thi-ap8:7.3":"Chadim karonto buddhassa, ","thi-ap8:7.4":"matthake dharayanti te. ","thi-ap8:8.1":"Udaggacitta sumana, ","thi-ap8:8.2":"vedajata katanjali; ","thi-ap8:8.3":"Tattha cittam pasadetva, ","thi-ap8:8.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","thi-ap8:9.1":"Mahanelassa chadanam, ","thi-ap8:9.2":"dharenti mama muddhani; ","thi-ap8:9.3":"Dibbagandham pavayami, ","thi-ap8:9.4":"sattuppalassidam phalam. ","thi-ap8:10.1":"Kadaci niyamanaya, ","thi-ap8:10.2":"natisanghena me tada; ","thi-ap8:10.3":"Yavata parisa mayham, ","thi-ap8:10.4":"mahanelam dhariyati. ","thi-ap8:11.1":"Sattatidevarajunam, ","thi-ap8:11.2":"mahesittamakarayim; ","thi-ap8:11.3":"Sabbattha issara hutva, ","thi-ap8:11.4":"samsarami bhavabhave. ","thi-ap8:12.1":"Tesatthi cakkavattinam, ","thi-ap8:12.2":"mahesittamakarayim; ","thi-ap8:12.3":"Sabbe mamanuvattanti, ","thi-ap8:12.4":"adeyyavacana ahum. ","thi-ap8:13.1":"Uppalasseva me vanno, ","thi-ap8:13.2":"gandho ceva pavayati; ","thi-ap8:13.3":"Dubbanniyam na janami, ","thi-ap8:13.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","thi-ap8:14.1":"Iddhipadesu kusala, ","thi-ap8:14.2":"bojjhangabhavanarata; ","thi-ap8:14.3":"Abhinnaparamippatta, ","thi-ap8:14.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","thi-ap8:15.1":"Satipatthanakusala, ","thi-ap8:15.2":"samadhijhanagocara; ","thi-ap8:15.3":"Sammappadhanamanuyutta, ","thi-ap8:15.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","thi-ap8:16.1":"Viriyam me dhuradhorayham, ","thi-ap8:16.2":"yogakkhemadhivahanam; ","thi-ap8:16.3":"Sabbasava parikkhina, ","thi-ap8:16.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","thi-ap8:17.1":"Ekatimse ito kappe, ","thi-ap8:17.2":"yam pupphamabhipujayim; ","thi-ap8:17.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","thi-ap8:17.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","thi-ap8:18.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","thi-ap8:18.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap8:18.3":"viharami anasava. ","thi-ap8:19.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","thi-ap8:19.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap8:19.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thi-ap8:20.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","thi-ap8:20.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap8:20.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","thi-ap8:21.1":"Ittham sudam sattuppalamalika bhikkhuni ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","thi-ap8:22.1":"Sattuppalamalikatheriyapadanam atthamam. "}